td.span: For the fifth year running, the NAMM Foundation has selected the Paoli Community School Corporation as one of theBest Communities for Music Education (BCME). Congratulations of all the music instructors who promote excellence in the area of music education. Special congratulations to all the students and parents who make music education a priority in their lives. We are #PaoliProud!
